      <PackageReleaseNotes>
      Adds minimal command support with fluent configuration

      Introduces a simplified command registration system allowing for quick command setup with  lambda expressions. This enhances developer experience by:

        - Adding a MinimalCommand class for lightweight command definitions
        - Implementing a fluent API for command configuration
        - Supporting both registry-based and minimal commands simultaneously
        - Making the ConsoleApplication instance accessible via static Current property

      Commands can now be added directly using AddCommand() with an action delegate, reducing  boilerplate compared to implementing full ICommand interfaces.
      </PackageReleaseNotes>
